:INFO
The First Report From the Other Side of the Opening
Gardens of the Moon begins in the middle of a siege with no introduction to the \
world, the military, or any character who will be important for the whole novel. \
Steven Erikson does not explain. He trusts that the world will cohere eventually \
and it does, but the first 200 pages require a tolerance for confusion that I \
had to actively practice. Once the pieces began to connect, around page 250, \
I understood why this series has the devoted readership it does.

